1
00:00:00,713 --> 00:00:03,546
This hall belongs to the church

2
00:00:05,922 --> 00:00:07,689
It was for religious ceremonies

3
00:00:08,657 --> 00:00:11,283
We would sit here on religious occasions

4
00:00:12,743 --> 00:00:14,516
There were seats

5
00:00:14,969 --> 00:00:17,103
There were control panels, lighting, and air conditioners

6
00:00:19,265 --> 00:00:21,424
And the bishop’s chairs

7
00:00:22,618 --> 00:00:26,976
Here was the bishop’s chair, and here was the patriarch’s chair

8
00:00:29,090 --> 00:00:31,836
Now it’s as you see in front of you

9
00:00:32,960 --> 00:00:34,914
Everything was here

10
00:00:36,348 --> 00:00:40,749
The sofas, the carpets, and the air conditioners

11
00:00:42,382 --> 00:00:43,496
