14
00:00:53,172 --> 00:00:56,339
No, I don’t know anything

15
00:00:56,800 --> 00:00:59,337
Interviewer: No—What?
Witness: I don’t know anything about this

16
00:00:59,790 --> 00:01:01,739
I don’t know what they did with it

17
00:01:03,652 --> 00:01:05,328
