18
00:01:09,088 --> 00:01:12,847
Interviewer: These burn marks on the walls, don’t you know what caused them?

19
00:01:12,899 --> 00:01:13,907
No, no

20
00:01:16,606 --> 00:01:17,868
They’re burned, but I don’t know

21
00:01:23,925 --> 00:01:25,892
Interviewer: So this hall was for celebrations?

22
00:01:25,990 --> 00:01:27,270
For religious celebrations

23
00:01:28,372 --> 00:01:30,490
Or if visitors came from outside

24
00:01:30,960 --> 00:01:34,074
Priests or bishops, we received them here
